                  </handDesc>
                  <additions>
                     <p>Hluti af handritinu (blöð í oktavó) er afrit af ýmsum skjölum bréfabókarinnar. Afrit þessi eru skrifuð í upphafi 18. aldar af skrifara <name key="ArnMag001" type="person">Árna Magnússonar</name> á bl. 3-10, 19-24, 26-31, 39-44, 91-94, 97-98, 116-121, 123-130, 136-145, 150-157, 164-167, 171-174, 176-183, 185-194, 199-200, 206-211, 213-216, 218-221, 223-225, 227-230, 241-244 eru.</p>
                  </additions>
                  <bindingDesc>
                     <binding notBefore="1961" notAfter="1961" contemporary="false">
                        <p>Band frá því í febrúar 1961.
 </p>
                     </binding>
                  </bindingDesc>
                  <accMat>
                     <p>Seðill með hendi <name key="ArnMag001" type="person">Árna Magnússonar</name> við bl. 11.</p>
                  </accMat>
